node.text:
Practice (1h 5m) Water still remains one of the most satisfying things to paint lmao. Really busy lately so I'm hoping to do more chill studies here this month. Speaking of studies if you're interested in learning how to turn a reference image into a good sketch I got a tutorial on that for August on my patreon! 10/10 will change ur life my patrons can confirm 🌞 will also be uploading this process there soon 
.
.
.

node.text:
Did some style study recently, practice video on my patreon! I focused on the Disney shape language in tangled, love the flow and expressiveness of their characters and thought it'd be cool to learn how they do it by trying to replicate things for myself! Rapunzel is the ref! 💛
.
I love art bc theres always more to learn 🥲
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
